#. type: Content of: <div><div><h1>
msgid "First time user?"
msgstr "¿Usuario por primera vez?"

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><ul><li>
msgid "If you don't know what a metadata or a man-in-the-middle attack is."
msgstr ""
"Si no sabes qué es un ataque de metadata o un ataque de intermediario (man-"
"in-the-middle)."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><ul><li>
msgid ""
"If you think no-one can eavesdrop on your communications because you are "
"using Tor."
msgstr "Si piensas que nadie puede espiar tus comunicaciones porque usas Tor."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><ul><li>
msgid "If you have no notion of how Tails works."
msgstr "Si no tienes idea sobre cómo funciona Tor."

#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><p>
msgid ""
"<strong>Then, check first the [[about]] and [[warning|doc/about/warning]] "
"pages to make sure that Tails is the right tool for you and that you "
"understand well its limitations.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong> Entonces, lee primero las páginas de [[about]] y "
"[[warning|doc/about/warning]] para asegurarte que Tails es la herramienta "
"apropiada para ti y que entiendes bien sus limitaciones.</strong>"

